UniTraj inference for PostGIS LINESTRING M

This product includes software adapted from the UniTraj research implementation:
https://github.com/Yasoz/UniTraj

Original work: "UniTraj: Learning a Universal Trajectory Foundation Model from
Billion-Scale Worldwide Traces" by Yuanshao Zhu, James Jianqiao Yu, Xiangyu
Zhao, Xun Zhou, Liang Han, Xuetao Wei, and Yuxuan Liang.

